packages/crypto/README.md
     1‚Üí# Enclosed crypto library
     3‚ÜíThis package contains the natives crypto primitives used by the [Enclosed lib and project](https://enclosed.cc). It is a standalone package built to provide compatibility between different environments by exposing the same API for node:crypto and web SubtleCrypto.
     4‚Üí
     5‚Üí## Installation
     7‚Üí```bash
     8‚Üí# with npm
     9‚Üínpm install @enclosed/crypto
    10‚Üí
    11‚Üí# with yarn
    12‚Üíyarn add @enclosed/crypto
    13‚Üí
    14‚Üí# with pnpm
    15‚Üípnpm add @enclosed/crypto
    16‚Üí```
    17‚Üí

